CONCEAL.COM, 6112 bytes of RAM; 03/08/91 07:28 


"conceal /?" returns:

CONCEAL 1.0 (c) 1990 Ziff Communications Co. 
PC Magazine þ Michael J. Mefford 
Syntax: Conceal [/P password] [filespec] [options] 
/S = Conceal filespec attribute [ON | OFF]; default = ON 
/F = File security toggle [ON | OFF]; default is ON 
/A = Attribute [+|-A] [+|-S] [+|-H] [+|-R] 
/N = New password 
/B = Hardware blank [nn][ON | OFF] 
/G = Graphic blank  [nn][ON | OFF] 
     nn = 0 - 60 minutes; 0 = OFF; default = 3 minutes, ON  
/O = Over-graphics blanking [ON | OFF]; default = ON        
/T = Password required to unblank [ON | OFF]; default = ON  
/H = Hotkey for immediate blank; Ctrl or Alt plus new hotkey
     eg. /H Ctrl Y or /H Alt 1;  default is Alt Z           
/U = Uninstall 
